<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BAWIPA BIA TUAH U CH7</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Iang ngei thiannak he Bawipa cu bia cio tuah u, A hmaiah kun in a
 sunparnak thanh, Toidornak le nawlngaihnak rimhmui thaw he cun, Ra u law
 Bawipa cu bia cio u si.

[V2]
 A kehram ah na thilrit cu rak thum tuah law, A zawnruahnak lungthin in
 an chan lai, Na ngaihchiatnak hnemh in na thlacam an leh lai, Na ca a
 thabik lam ah na hruai lai.

[V3]
 A hmai ka hung panh awkah na zakzum hlah seh, Na tenpamnak ruangah na
 lung der hlah, A biatak le velngeih zawnruah dawtnak ruangah, A
 hmunthiang ah umnak nawl na ngei lai.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<hymn_number>7</hymn_number>
</song>